/~loaded bat/spells

; Bad things

/red "^You stutter the magic words and fail the spell\.$"
/red "^Your mind plays a trick with you and you fail in your spell\.$"
/red "^You fail miserably in your spell\.$"
/red "^Something touches you and spoils your concentration ruining the spell\.$"
/red "^Your concentration fails and so does your spell\.$"
/red "^You poke yourself in the eye and your spell misfires\.$"
/red "^Your spell just sputters\.$"
/red "^You are disturbed by something, your spell misfires\.$"
/red "^You falter and fumble the spell\. Amazingly it fires upon (.*)$"
/red "^You fail to reach (.*)\.$"
/red "^You fail to get anything useful done\.$"

; Good things

;/green "^You feel like (.*) healed you a bit\.$" -F autothankheal = /repeat -06 1 /send bat Thanks %{P1}!
;/green " heals (.*) of your wounds\.$" -F autothankhealme = /repeat -10 1 /send tell %{P1} Thanks for healing me %{P2} of the way!
/green "^You feel like (.*) healed you a bit\.$"
/green " heals (.*) of your wounds\.$"
/green "^You heal (.*) of your wounds\.$"
/green "^You harm (.*)\.$"
/green "^You finish meditating and get to your feet, feeling more chaotic\.$"
/green "^Your Infernal Sword materializes in your hands\.$"
/green "^Your Infernal Sword begins to shed a harsh black aura\.$"
/green "^You watch with selfpride as your (.*) hits"

